---
// Not Found (404) Page
---

<section class="min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-24 bg-background">
  <div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-primary text-[120px] font-bold font-serif leading-tight mb-4">404</p>
    <h1 class="text-[36px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-6">Page not found</h1>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-10">Sorry, we couldn't find the page you're looking for.</p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[14px] hover:bg-primary-hover transition-colors">
      Go back home
    </a>
  </div>
</section>